        <div class="mx-auto px-4 py-4 container-fluid">
            <h3 id="registration-form">Register to create your Moreland Photography Studio account</h3>
            <p>Please enter your details below to create your new Moreland Photography Studio account. This page uses the bcrypt JavaScript library to create a hashed version of each user password, which is then saved in an SQLite database alongside the user's account details. This ensures a high level of password security as it stores the password as an irreversibly obfuscated version of itself, which can only be replicated by an identical password and cannot be transformed back into the original password. Due to this practice, if the Moreland Photography Studio user database were ever accessed by an unauthorised entity, the hashed user passwords would not allow them to access any accounts.</p>
            <div class="mx-2 px-2 mb-4 pb-4">
                <form action="/register" method="post">
                    <div class="row mt-2">
                        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                            <label for="email" class="my-1">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" name="email" id="email" class="form-control">
                            
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                            <label for="password" class="my-1">Password</label>
                            <input type="password" name="password" id="password" minlength="8" class="form-control">
                        </div>
                    </div>
    
                    <div class="row my-2">
                        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                            <label for="fname" class="my-1">First Name</label>
                            <input type="text" name="fname" id="fname" class="form-control">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                            <label for="lname" class="my-1">Last Name</label>
                            <input type="text" name="lname" id="lname" class="form-control">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                
                    <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-block m-auto p-auto">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Register</button>
                    </div>
                    
                </form>
                
         
            </div>

        </div>



        
    
